es 4 mounted maps, and many scenarios that are each given their own scenario cards (ala the US Squad Leader wargame). Includes slightly larger counters than are usually used in Japanese wargames.\n\nThere was an expansion/sequel to this produced.\n\n	120	120	120	1984	2	2	2	Yasunori Sekiyama	Hobby Japan
