ain type of challenge, if a challenger wins he can trade colored pawns with the loser of the challenge, which not only affects his position on the board, but can earn him bonus points if that person got lots of votes in his speaking rounds.\n\n	60	60	60	2002	3	6	6	Michael A. Stusser	Bensussen Deutsch and Associates
